 In particular, we can try to apply the equation 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}u=f$
\end_inset

, noting that 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}$
\end_inset

 is an operator acting on 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{x}$
\end_inset

