\begin_inset Formula \[
\hat{A}u=\int_{\Omega}d^{d}\vec{x}'[\hat{A}G(\vec{x},\vec{x}')]f(\vec{x}')=f(\vec{x}).\]

\end_inset

This is telling us that 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{A}G(\vec{x},\vec{x}')$
\end_inset

